{"tid":323003,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"京都行程求救","createTime":"2017-07-15T09:29:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-17T09:24:50.000Z","uid":3164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"262a46080c3ad662dd966068a1d05821e4a65b4e","tid":323003,"uid":3164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T09:29:05.000Z","msg":"是咁的 黎緊11月17-24會去關西旅行<br />\n其他日子都諗到個行程係點 係差18-21呢幾日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為我地唔係跑check point 嗰啲<br />\n而女朋友又冇特別想睇啲乜野咁<br />\n所以大約安排左行程如下<br />\n18/11 京都單車遊？（可能係市內漫無目的咁踩，但又想搵啲野睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n19/11伏見，清水寺，三十三間堂<br />\n20/11嵐山 （想坐激流睇紅葉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n21/11 奈良》大阪<br />\n<br />\n其實主要日子都諗好 係得番18唔知做乜好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  唔踩單車嘅話去宇治？ <br />\n<br />\n感謝咁多位巴絲賜教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"056b99aa2ee40503a32417be428a751bf8d474b3","tid":323003,"uid":36034,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T18:24:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>是咁的 黎緊11月17-24會去關西旅行<br />\n其他日子都諗到個行程係點 係差18-21呢幾日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為我地唔係跑check point 嗰啲<br />\n而女朋友又冇特別想睇啲乜野咁<br />\n所以大約安排左行程如下<br />\n18/11 京都單車遊？（可能係市內漫無目的咁踩，但又想搵啲野睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n19/11伏見，清水寺，三十三間堂<br />\n20/11嵐山 （想坐激流睇紅葉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n21/11 奈良》大阪<br />\n<br />\n其實主要日子都諗好 係得番18唔知做乜好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  唔踩單車嘅話去宇治？ <br />\n<br />\n感謝咁多位巴絲賜教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n可以去大原，坐巴士好似半個鐘鬆d，有三千院可以坐低欣賞園景再飲杯茶，之後有味噌地雞煲同溫泉浸，輕鬆大半日行程<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/16/022351_921a1718e30916a962341bf7ed1b1f27.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F16%2F022351_921a1718e30916a962341bf7ed1b1f27.jpg&h=3c4426f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/16/022351_51e9f34ab95a25c0f888cb861a4e2ca8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F16%2F022351_51e9f34ab95a25c0f888cb861a4e2ca8.jpg&h=e959f170&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/16/022352_51e9f34ab95a25c0f888cb861a4e2ca8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F16%2F022352_51e9f34ab95a25c0f888cb861a4e2ca8.jpg&h=0a1046d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/16/022352_eaeef7e658ab90da5566edd7dae96bd2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F16%2F022352_eaeef7e658ab90da5566edd7dae96bd2.jpg&h=99ead026&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"962eae7261d6c1209435a205a428338179dcc7df","tid":323003,"uid":73231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T18:57:42.000Z","msg":"搭單問<br />\n我同朋友都去過京都 又冇乜興緻去著和服<br />\n我哋會住一晚就走 趕住搭新幹線去東京<br />\n之前住嗰晚住大阪<br />\n<br />\n宇治值唔值得去？定去多次嵐山？<br />\n定留喺大阪行吓街先過去？<br />\n<br />\n大家都好怕蝗<br />\n所以想盡量避開啲多蝗區<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c20ff122b2784374a0c2e516d475d8548a2c41e6","tid":323003,"uid":3164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T01:56:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>搭單問<br />\n我同朋友都去過京都 又冇乜興緻去著和服<br />\n我哋會住一晚就走 趕住搭新幹線去東京<br />\n之前住嗰晚住大阪<br />\n<br />\n宇治值唔值得去？定去多次嵐山？<br />\n定留喺大阪行吓街先過去？<br />\n<br />\n大家都好怕蝗<br />\n所以想盡量避開啲多蝗區<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n宇治唔知但嵐山一定多蝗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c26ab615d70f13d185ad64ebc8d156edfd6668fa","tid":323003,"uid":45760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T03:19:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 幾多人一齊，鐘意shopping 定睇景？"},{"pid":"28a00f94459034039a731abfd75fb7b317df21f2","tid":323003,"uid":3164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T06:11:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 幾多人一齊，鐘意shopping 定睇景？</blockquote><br />\n得我同女朋友兩個<br />\nShopping 諗住去到大阪先 同埋17號都會行下河原町 所以淨低幾日唔會點諗shopping<br />\n主要想睇紅葉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b41e815b3f43a049416d0b62f26502e843f488d","tid":323003,"uid":61586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T06:41:05.000Z","msg":"去保津川記得著多件衫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係架野度凍兩個鐘都幾和味"},{"pid":"48aa2607e208d348e1f2ab7502294973d0fba94c","tid":323003,"uid":3164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T07:39:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去保津川記得著多件衫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係架野度凍兩個鐘都幾和味</blockquote><br />\n會唔會彈到濕曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d053743130acfc5611f4a3feb65c69daa53bab7","tid":323003,"uid":58911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T09:24:50.000Z","msg":"去宇治<br />\n好休閒"}]}